PHASE 1

The Community

The M.O team is mainly made up of (different sectors) investors. As investors we understand the struggles and fears of investing. Therefore, we are building a project that would benefit to everybody regardless of your expertise, skills, etc. The Majestic Owl is a project built with the community and for the community. Because this is OUR project. Since day one we’ve been giving and rewarding the most dedicated Owlers to prove our involvement to not only the project but also to every member. Our goal is to all together help every dedicated member to reach its ultimate goal of investing, as this project has been made to be profitable to everybody. 

PHASE 2

M.O Mobile App

We are also building The Majestic Owl Mobile app. It will be available to be downloaded on the play and App Store. We want to give a real utility to your NFT, therefore we are creating a platform where you will be able to use your NFT in a smart  and interactive way. We want to make this project easy to manage and understandable for all. Through the Majestic Owl Mobile app, you will have easy access to the project and clear overview of your assets. 

PHASE 3

First journey to rewards in the METAVERSE

Your owl is going on journeys in the Metaverse to come back with rewards (based on its rarity). Via the M.O. Mobile app you will be able to monthly deploy and send your Owl on missions for rewards. What can he get you ? Perkament rolls(clues for rewarded riddles), Real life usable goods (film ticket, coupons, etc.), An amount of Crypto, An amount of Cash, Real life merchandise (plush,clothing piece,etc.), A valuable luxury item (Rolex,designer shoes, etc.), Car keys (Tesla, etc.), high valued NFT assets (nft, sandbox land, etc.), many more...

PHASE 4

Increase your investment significantly (burn process)

As stated before, we want to give the opportunity to every investor to propulse their investment journey through this project. By investing in the Majestic Owl NFT you are acquiring an NFT that you will be able to auto-manage to increase its value. You will have the possibility to directly influence the value of your NFT through the burn process and 2x, 5x, 10x and more your investment. By breeding two first generation Owls, you will generate a second generation Majestic Owl which is automatically more rare and more valuable than a basic 1st generation Owl. 

PHASE 5

Exclusive accessibilities

We as, investors want to put all our experience, contacts and connections to give you the best opportunities to succeed in that mission.  Your M.O NFT will be an entry ticket to exclusive accessibilities. You will have the possibility to have your personal projects supported by us, not only financially but also strategically. You will have access to private groups for the Majestic Owl holders only, where very high value information will be shared. You will be able to stack your investment and make passive returns. You will have access to trainings and advices on trading, investment and business creation.

PHASE 6

Second collection launch « Consumables & Crows »

The Owl’s journeys in the METAVERSE are getting more intense. We are launching a second collection of antagonists to our Owls. It’s time for the Ravens(the enemies of the Owls) to invade the METAVERSE and oppose our friendly Owlers. That means, play to earn through in flight combats, confrontations and clashes. You will also be able to equip, upgrade and strengthen your Owl through consumables. [object Object] DISCLAIMER: Only holders of The M.O. first collection NFTs will be eligible to mint assets from the second collection.

PHASE 7

METAVERSE VR experience.

Imagine taking a flight with your friendly Owl in the air and visualize the Metaverse from a different perspective. Diligently explore, but not only, fight your enemies for cash prizes and more rewards, through a realistic VR experience. 

PHASE 8

Save our planet

We are planning to plant a minimum of 100,000 trees throughout this year. By planting trees the Majestic Owl will actively participate into ecological advancement and so fulfill the « Save our Planet » initiative by reducing the human’s ecological footprint. Planting trees will contribute in naturally clean the air, help the soil recover, mitigate the effects of droughts, many more… We will associate and invest in charities such as; "OneTreePlanted" & "Woodland Trust".

PHASE 9

Access to Majestic events around the world

The Majestic Owl will hold public and private events in the most famous cities of the world. Investment seminaries hold by some of the greatest in business. Yacht parties with celebrities and influencers, celebrations and much more. Your Majestic Owl NFT will be a free ticket to participate in these worldwide events. In this project the community is king. We will organize a lot of events in order to connect and vibe in a Majestic spirit.
